org.openimaj.ml.timeseries.processor

Interface TimeSeriesProcessor<ALLDATA,SINGLEDATA,TIMESERIES extends TimeSeries<ALLDATA,SINGLEDATA,TIMESERIES>>

  • Type Parameters:
    ALLDATA - The type of the data as a collection
    SINGLEDATA - the type of an individual unit of data
    TIMESERIES - the time series returned by the various TimeSeries.get(long) functions
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    GaussianTimeSeriesProcessor, IntervalSummationProcessor, LinearInterpolationProcessor, LinearRegressionProcessor, MovingAverageProcessor, TimeSeriesInterpolation, WindowedLinearRegressionProcessor
